{"tid":2166212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官方微博發佈推薦「黃店」貼文被質疑支持「港獨」，崇光百貨：不是故意發佈，已刪除","createTime":"2020-08-20T09:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T10:53:13.000Z","uid":212249,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb17cd0426bdcf8543206ec0a4a0672ef21cbba","tid":2166212,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"【環球網報道】今天（18日）16時，香港崇光百貨官方微博發佈了一條推薦餐館的貼文，結果被網民質疑「撐黃店」、「支持&lsquo;港獨&rsquo;」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YxNdJLt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxNdJLt.png&h=e1f25eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引發質疑的是，該條貼文的配圖中包括兩張貼滿便利貼的圖片，圖中的便利貼上寫有「反修例」口號，支持暴徒，辱罵港警等內容，還有疑似寫有「港獨」標語的便利貼。<br />\n<br />\n在該條貼文的評論區，有網民留言質問，發這標語是什麼意思？來宣傳「黃店」？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdbiaqD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOdbiaqD.png&h=6a9e61ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民認為這是「故意挑釁」，還有人質疑「崇光百貨公然支持&lsquo;港獨&rsquo;」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OicdJLO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOicdJLO.png&h=482ac30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在發佈不到1個小時後，香港崇光百貨官方微博的頁面中已找不到上述貼文。<br />\n<br />\n環球網記者18日就此事撥通了香港崇光百貨官方微博備注的聯繫方式，對方告訴記者，並沒有「撐黃店」，官微上此前就發佈過推薦餐廳的內容。已向相關部門同事瞭解此事，不是故意發佈該條微博貼文，目前已經刪除。"},{"pid":"d50ca7c1a17fb3b70ae2fd86c56a95f54567e3fa","tid":2166212,"uid":113185,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"崇光好勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身在藍營心在黃 希望兩邊都做唔起然後執左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a7dbb77c63ab0019310d3a02b6f0acb483ebcb","tid":2166212,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"宣傳自己租戶都唔得"},{"pid":"2684fcfdd5ad7f0ae7d3487e4248a880a817cf6c","tid":2166212,"uid":127454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"人家都說了只是心願便利貼 不是黃屍文宣 為何要批鬥支持祖國的藍色商戶SOGO??"},{"pid":"eb5bec7de0a0513b1cf9201d4cc81b89fe5e3a56","tid":2166212,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"sogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪去thankful<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}